Loan Agent System
A modular, professional loan management frontend built for scalability, clarity, and modern enterprise needs.

Overview
Loan Agent System is a responsive, multi-role solution for tracking, requesting, approving, and analyzing loans in a business or institutional setting.

Designed in pure HTML, CSS, and JavaScript, the project is highly maintainable and ready to plug into any backend or cloud provider.

Features
Role-Based Dashboards:
Separate interfaces for Borrower, Lender, and Admin with workflow-specific tools.

Modern Authentication:
Secure login and signup experience.

Dynamic Loan Management:
Submit loan requests, approve loans, track repayments, view histories.

Live Statistics:
Admin dashboard shows user/loan metrics and recent activities.

Advanced UI/UX:
Mobile-ready, background branding, animated cursor, floating tips.

Extensible Architecture:
Each module/component in its own file for easy upgrades.

Local Demo (Production-Ready Structure):
State managed in browser for demo; easily connect to a backend as needed.
